<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2006/aug/21/warcrimes" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2006/aug/21/warcrimes" rel="nofollow">"Mladic shadow hangs over Srebrenica trial"</a>. 2006-08-21<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2006/aug/21/warcrimes" class="external free" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2006/aug/21/warcrimes" rel="nofollow">http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2006/aug/21/warcrimes</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-11-01</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Mladic+shadow+hangs+over+Srebrenica+trial&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2006-08-21&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Fworld%2F2006%2Faug%2F21%2Fwarcrimes&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Srebrenica_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
