<li id="cite_note-Post_Aug06-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Post_Aug06_2-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFCorder2006">Corder, Mike (2006-08-20). <a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/20/AR2006082000360.html" class="external text" title="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/20/AR2006082000360.html" rel="nofollow">"Srebrenica Genocide Trial to Restart"</a>. Associated Press<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/20/AR2006082000360.html" class="external free" title="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/20/AR2006082000360.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/20/AR2006082000360.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-11-01</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Srebrenica+Genocide+Trial+to+Restart&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Corder&amp;rft.aufirst=Mike&amp;rft.au=Corder%2C+Mike&amp;rft.date=2006-08-20&amp;rft.pub=Associated+Press&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwp-dyn%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2F2006%2F08%2F20%2FAR2006082000360.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Srebrenica_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
